Adisucipto, Kebon Roek, Ampenan | Depan Anjani oleh-oleh/timur pasar kebon roek, Mataram, Lombok 83511, Indonesia Location: Asia  >  Indonesia  >  West Nusa Tenggara  >  Lombok  >  Mataram Phone Number: 6281805245541 Ayam Taliwang is made with chicken (preferably free range), which is cut and cleaned prior to grilling. Once it has been grilled halfway, it is removed from the grill and tenderized with a pestle.
